WEBVTT

00:10:29.760 --> 00:10:33.096
with opportunity and economic mobility.

00:10:33.120 --> 00:10:35.296
Saudi Arabia has raised living standards

00:10:35.320 --> 00:10:38.576
while frustrating
many other human strivings.

00:10:38.600 --> 00:10:41.376
Two countries, both wealthy,

00:10:41.400 --> 00:10:43.120
not equally well off.

00:10:43.880 --> 00:10:48.216
And this brings me
to the challenge that we face today,

00:10:48.240 --> 00:10:50.376
the challenge that
automation poses for us.

00:10:50.400 --> 00:10:52.856
The challenge is not
that we're running out of work.

00:10:52.880 --> 00:10:54.816
The US has added 14 million jobs

00:10:54.840 --> 00:10:56.976
since the depths of the Great Recession.

00:10:57.000 --> 00:10:59.536
The challenge is that many of those jobs

00:10:59.560 --> 00:11:00.856
are not good jobs,